token_info.name: Título Rester/Restar - Luxemburgo Chair
token_info.description: 3d object used in animation and photomontages in the project "Rest_er - Rest_ar", unfolding of photographs proposed for an exhibition, which is now also transported to the virtual world, thus completing the range of meanings that the project proposes. 3d object of Chair based on the chairs of the Luxembourg Garden, Paris. These chairs are loose in the garden, freely moved in a constant reconfiguration of the space.
